{"tid":260244,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【好撚柒呀】有無窿被我捐","createTime":"2017-05-27T14:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T15:40:55.000Z","uid":9767,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0134a2ff3d7a56f0a77e1ea05978a0f11b2273","tid":260244,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:31:23.000Z","msg":"今日食茶餐廳 我話要杯熱咖啡 <br />\nME：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n伙記：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：熱咖啡唔該<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：ok 汪明荃係咪？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：？？(黑鬼問號)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：汪明荃？(望住我講)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：(心諗：呢條友做咩撚)<br />\n<br />\n然後我回左句：羅家英 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟手全場笑我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母擺明落我面 我即刻猛然企起身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後扮去廁所 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個伙記成手紋身 我撚敢出聲咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d42ff43708dab1d22d0b434d6